    "The studied models compared DL and ML approaches for miRNA-target prediction.",
    "The DL approach was found to be more accurate and precise than the ML approach.",
    "Another studied paper proposed an LSTM for biomedical named entity recognition, which outperformed traditional ML algorithms in accuracy.",
    "Another study focused on developing an amino acid encoding method for DL applications in bioinformatics.",
    "The method improved prediction accuracy for protein sequence classification."
